Obstacle - application中的类
The Obstacle class represents an obstacle in the robot arena.
Obstacle(int, int) - 类的构造器 application.Obstacle
Constructs a new Obstacle object with specified position and default color (black).
Obstacle(int, int, Color) - 类的构造器 application.Obstacle
Constructs a new Obstacle object with specified position and color.
obstacles - 类中的变量 application.RobotArena
A list of obstacles in the arena.
obstacles - 类中的静态变量 application.SensorRobot
A set of points representing the coordinates of obstacles that the SensorRobot must avoid.
onUpdateCallback - 类中的变量 application.RobotArena
A callback function that is invoked when the arena state changes, typically used to update the UI.
openArena() - 类中的方法 application.Main
Allows the user to open a saved arena profile.
